		<article>
			<h1 class="storytitle"><a href="http://markos.gaivo.net/blog/?p=257" rel="bookmark">Twitter</a></h1>

			<div class="post-text">
				<p>I have ignored <a class="zem_slink" title="Twitter" rel="homepage" href="http://www.twitter.com" target="_blank">Twitter</a> for a long time until it became obvious to me that lots of interesting stuff moved there and can&#8217;t be easily found elsewhere. So I made <a title="My twitter home" href="http://twitter.com/samastur">my home</a> to make following others easier and occasionally tweet something myself.</p>
<p>So far I haven&#8217;t really got a hang of it yet and my stream is as boring as it gets. Hopefully this is not a sign of things to come.</p>
